605
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:43,260
Lui ra đi.

606
00:38:43,770 --> 00:38:44,470
Vâng.

607
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:39,420
Hai ngươi,

608
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:40,070
đi xem thử.

609
00:40:40,180 --> 00:40:40,980
- Vâng.
- Vâng.

610
00:41:05,280 --> 00:41:05,990
Nói,

611
00:41:06,020 --> 00:41:07,750
